song.info:
Cosmic Octane
by
RabiteMan / Pulse Music
Greetings all...
This song was originally my entry for GroovyCompo 2, but I missed the deadline and the song was never released (or quite finished, for that matter).
But here it is, just as I left it. I felt it was good enough to release, even though it is so short. It's a short download though.
All samples are by Hunz.
Bye now
